Usage: get_lib_pg_pins [-help] [-filter <expr>] { -of_objects <object_list> }

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
-filter <expr>                # Filters the collection with the specified
                              # expression (string, optional)
-of_objects <object_list>     # Creates a collection of all library pg pins
                              # associated with the specified library cells
                              # (string, optional)